Github Widget modules allows you to show github information on Drupal nodes.

Installation
------------

1) Download the github api at https://github.com/ornicar/php-github-api and place it in the github_widget directory. You can ?q=admin/reports/status to see if the library is in the right place.

2) Enable the module

3) Go to the config page and enable the github widget for one or more content types

4) Create a node and fill the username of the github repository and the name of the repository.

5) Save the node and you should see information from your repository on your node.

